					<div class="commentsubject">Subject: <span>Re: What's wrong?</span><br /></div>
					<div class="commentbody"><div class='commentquote'>Guest wrote:<div class='commentquotebody'>It got so thick (almost looked crumbly) that the blender was laboring before even half the amount of oil was added.  He continued to add the rest of the oil slowly and it turned runny.  What did he do wrong?</div></div><br />
